data.description: Welcome to this unbelievable home that allows you and your family to enjoy a spacious, renovated home just a few minutes away from the exciting Prasada Gateway. With easy access to brand new shopping, dining, and entertainment options, you'll never run out of things to do. Plus, the home is situated close to trails, parks, and plenty of green spaces, making it an ideal location for those who love spending time outdoors. Call now for a full list of upgrades, you will be WOWed!
